      • findPost

        public Post findPost​(java.lang.String fileName)
        Method to find the a post in the user's list of post based on the filename. Posts with the same name are different if they have different filenames
        Parameters:
        fileName - the filename of the post being searched for.
        Returns:
        returns the post with a matching filename
